423
00:26:31.092 --> 00:26:34.529
And I expect you to let me
run my ranch as I see fit.

424
00:26:34.595 --> 00:26:36.931
<i>No surprises. Beulah.</i>

425
00:26:36.997 --> 00:26:39.233
