469
00:29:11.018 --> 00:29:14.922
'Cause I promise you.
you won't.

470
00:29:15.657 --> 00:29:17.358
But he might.

471
00:29:19.527 --> 00:29:21.795
[sobbing]

472
00:29:24.198 --> 00:29:25.600
Now go on. just put it down.

473
00:29:26.500 --> 00:29:27.901
Now. go on and give me the gun.
