622
00:40:32.465 --> 00:40:34.969
Sort of. yeah.

623
00:40:35.036 --> 00:40:37.071
You want to go back?

624
00:40:37.138 --> 00:40:39.173
I do...

625
00:40:39.240 --> 00:40:40.473
