Don't be scared.

632
00:41:57.184 --> 00:41:58.586
Uh...

633
00:41:59.353 --> 00:42:00.855
I'm not.

634
00:42:07.528 --> 00:42:09.096
You are.

635
00:42:25.679 --> 00:42:26.947
[chuckles]

636
00:42:27.782 --> 00:42:29.016
